  "title": "Indoor Sales Executive (Freight Forwarding / Marymount MRT / 5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle sales inquiries, prepare and present competitive quotations to prospective clients</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively and professionally with both external clients and internal teams</li>\n  <li>Develop and implement sales strategies and marketing plans to drive business growth</li>\n  <li>Deliver high-quality customer service to ensure satisfaction and foster long-term client relationships</li>\n  <li>Conduct follow-ups on cold leads to generate new business opportunities and meet sales targets</li>\n  <li>Compile and submit monthly sales reports to track performance and support decision-making</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**Must be available to meet clients as needed (<strong>Company car provided in the office; Class 3 driving license required</strong>).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
